== DESCRIPTION

A collection of command line tools written in Boo:
* filetypes: prints all filetypes present in the current directory and below
* guid: prints a new GUID, in uppercase or lowercase and with or without dashes
* matches: highlights all regular expression matches in a given string
* rn: renames files using regular expressions
* split: splits every line from standard input using a regular expression and prints the result

